data.description: Discover luxury living in this 2023-built home boasting amazing pond views. This 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence combines modern elegance with the tranquility of its natural surroundings. With 3 bedrooms conveniently located on one level, this home offers a practical and family-friendly layout. The primary suite provides a serene retreat with its private bath and generous sized walk in closet, and airy space. The open kitchen and dining area, equipped with modern appliances, seamlessly connect to create an ideal space for entertaining. Step outside to a backyard oasis where the pond becomes a captivating focal point for relaxation and outdoor activities.  Immerse yourself in the lifestyle you deserve—schedule a private showing today to experience the magic of this home!
